-- |

-- This module defines a table of all
-- predefined XML entity references

module Text.XML.HXT.Parser.XmlEntities
    ( xmlEntities
    )

where

-- ------------------------------------------------------------

-- |
-- list of predefined XML entity names and their unicode values

xmlEntities     :: [(String, Int)]

                  , ("lt",      60)
                  , ("gt",      62)
                  , ("apos",    39)
                  ]
